ACTION: List all processes
COMMAND: ps aux | grep -E "uvicorn|next" | grep -v grep

ACTION: Summary report
COMMAND: cat << 'EOF'

================================================================================
🎉 FEATURELAB MVP - DEPLOYMENT READY
================================================================================

✅ BACKEND (FastAPI)
   Location: ./backend
   Server: http://localhost:8000
   Health: curl http://localhost:8000/health
   Status: RUNNING

✅ FRONTEND (Next.js)
   Location: ./frontend
   Server: http://localhost:3000
   Status: RUNNING

✅ DATABASE
   Provider: Neon PostgreSQL
   Tables: experiments, features
   Status: CONNECTED

✅ AI INTEGRATIONS
   Gemini: Configured
   Pinecone: Configured
   Status: READY

================================================================================
🚀 DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS
================================================================================

DEPLOY TO VERCEL (Frontend):
   1. Push to GitHub: git push origin main
   2. Visit vercel.com, import project
   3. Set NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL env var
   4. Deploy automatically

DEPLOY TO RENDER (Backend):
   1. Push to GitHub
   2. Visit render.com, create Web Service
   3. Point to this repo
   4. Set environment variables:
      - DATABASE_URL
      - PINECONE_API_KEY
      - GEMINI_API_KEY
      - PINECONE_INDEX=featurelab-prod
   5. Deploy

================================================================================
📊 FEATURE ENGINEERING AGENT LOOP
================================================================================

The agent implements this autonomous cycle:

1. OBSERVE   → Profile feature distribution & correlations
2. HYPOTHESIZE → Use Gemini to propose transformations
3. EXECUTE   → Apply top-2 transformations
4. EVALUATE  → Score on MI, IV, single-feature AUC
5. DECIDE    → Keep if improvement > 2%, else iterate
6. INTERACT  → Create interactions between top features
7. COMPARE   → Final baseline comparison
8. SAVE      → Persist if AUC improvement > 1.5%

================================================================================
📁 PROJECT STRUCTURE
================================================================================

FeatureLab/
├── backend/
│   ├── main.py          (FastAPI server)
│   ├── agent.py         (Agentic loop)
│   ├── tools.py         (Feature engineering tools)
│   ├── models.py        (Pydantic models)
│   ├── database.py      (Neon + SQLAlchemy)
│   ├── embedding.py     (Pinecone integration)
│   ├── llm.py           (Gemini integration)
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   ├── .env
│   └── venv/
│
├── frontend/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── page.tsx         (Landing - hero, CTA, features)
│   │   ├── dashboard/page.tsx (Agent UI - upload, run, results)
│   │   ├── layout.tsx
│   │   └── globals.css
│   ├── components/
│   ├── package.json
│   ├── tailwind.config.ts
│   ├── tsconfig.json
│   └── .env.local
│
├── .vercelrc
├── vercel.json
├── Procfile
├── render.yaml
├── .gitignore
└── README.md

================================================================================
✨ NEXT STEPS
================================================================================

1. Test locally:
   - Visit http://localhost:3000 (landing page)
   - Click "Launch App" → /dashboard
   - Upload sample CSV and watch agent run

2. Deploy to Vercel + Render:
   - Push to GitHub
   - Connect in Vercel & Render dashboards
   - Set environment variables
   - Deploy automatically

3. Monitor & iterate:
   - Check /api/experiments for runs
   - Review engineered features in database
   - Adjust evaluation_threshold as needed

================================================================================

